Love from Kolkata!

snippet.textDisplay:
There was a time when Umair Jaswal was a local singer in Islamabad, and I would go to his concerts, paying 100 to 250 and 500rs, and he would literally dance all over the stage, so energetic and nice person he was and still is. Qayaas was his band.
I was in his concert in Kuch Khas Islamabad feb in 2013, and Qayaas was about to perform all the other members were on the stage and the music started playing, Umair wasnt there, and I looked beside me and he was standing right beside me in the crowd, I looked at him and he was smiling and was like shhhhh,  and then he just stormed unto the stage. We headbanged to his songs, and enjoyed alot. Amazing Guy.
